# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# vLLM DGX Spark Configuration — Qwen3.5-397B-A17B (INT4 AWQ)
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# MoE flagship: 397B total / 17B active params. Apache 2.0 license.
# BF16 ≈ 794 GB, FP8 ≈ 397 GB (both far too large) → INT4 AWQ ≈ 100 GB.
# Tight fit on single B200 — requires aggressive quantization and short
# context, but delivers the full Qwen3.5 frontier intelligence.
# Strengths: AIME 2026 91.3, SWE-bench 76.4, IFBench 76.5 (#1 instruction
#            following), 262K native context, 201 languages, natively
#            multimodal, strongest open-weight model available.
# Released: 2026-02-16
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Required for Multi-Node                                                 │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
WORKER_HOST="${WORKER_HOST:-}"
WORKER_IB_IP="${WORKER_IB_IP:-}"
WORKER_USER="${WORKER_USER:-$(whoami)}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Model Settings                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
# Use a community AWQ INT4 checkpoint (verify exact repo on HuggingFace)
MODEL="${MODEL:-Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-AWQ}"

# Single B200 — INT4 weights ≈ 100 GB, tight fit
TENSOR_PARALLEL="${TENSOR_PARALLEL:-1}"

# Push utilization to 0.95 to maximize usable memory
GPU_MEMORY_UTIL="${GPU_MEMORY_UTIL:-0.95}"

# Very limited KV cache headroom — keep context conservative
MAX_MODEL_LEN="${MAX_MODEL_LEN:-16384}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Docker Settings                                                         │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_IMAGE="${VLLM_IMAGE:-nvcr.io/nvidia/vllm:26.03-py3}"
HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME="${HEAD_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-head}"
WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME="${WORKER_CONTAINER_NAME:-ray-worker}"
SHM_SIZE="${SHM_SIZE:-16g}"
RAY_VERSION="${RAY_VERSION:-2.54.0}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Network Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
VLLM_PORT="${VLLM_PORT:-8000}"
RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT="${RAY_DASHBOARD_PORT:-8265}"
RAY_PORT="${RAY_PORT:-6385}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Storage Settings                                                        │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_CACHE="${HF_CACHE:-/raid/hf-cache}"
WORKER_HF_CACHE="${WORKER_HF_CACHE:-${HF_CACHE}}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ Authentication                                                          │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
HF_TOKEN="${HF_TOKEN:-}"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ vLLM Options                                                            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
# MoE model — enable expert parallelism
ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL="${ENABLE_EXPERT_PARALLEL:-true}"

SWAP_SPACE="${SWAP_SPACE:-16}"
TRUST_REMOTE_CODE="${TRUST_REMOTE_CODE:-false}"
LOAD_FORMAT="${LOAD_FORMAT:-safetensors}"

# AWQ quantization on a pre-quantized checkpoint; FP8 KV cache to save mem;
# Qwen3 reasoning parser + tool calling
EXTRA_ARGS="--quantization awq --kv-cache-dtype fp8 --reasoning-parser qwen3 --enable-auto-tool-choice --tool-call-parser qwen3_coder"

# ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
# │ NCCL/InfiniBand Settings (auto-detected, override if needed)            │
# └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
NCCL_DEBUG="${NCCL_DEBUG:-WARN}"
